// Trims insignificant zeros, e.g., replaces 1.2000k with 1.2k.
export default function(s){out:for(var n=s.length,i=1,i0=-1,i1;i<n;++i){switch(s[i]){case".":i0=i1=i;break;case"0":if(i0===0)i0=i;i1=i;break;default:if(!+s[i])break out;if(i0>0)i0=0;break;}}return i0>0?s.slice(0,i0)+s.slice(i1+1):s;}
